title: (Fri Full Show) Parker McCollum In-Studio On Something He Did Recently That He Regrets and His Career Goals + Bobby Answers The Five Most Googled Questions About Him + Amy Answers Listeners Voicemail Questions!
itunes:title: (Fri Full Show) Parker McCollum In-Studio On Something He Did Recently That He Regrets and His Career Goals + Bobby Answers The Five Most Googled Questions About Him + Amy Answers Listeners Voicemail Questions!
description:
Parker McCollum is in-studio with us! He talks about what his fans have done while he's performing, his career goals, his process behind writing songs and find out what he recently did that he regrets. Plus, Eddie asks Bobby the five most Googled questions about him. He answers them and says if they are true or false. Then, we listen to our voicemail and Amy answers listeners questions they have for her.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
